readable.content: A boy wearing a brown shirt and hat sits on a box next to a girl in front of a store . A girl with a toboggan and sunglasses smiles with her friend in the background as they do crafts . Some teenagers smile from an outdoor table . Ther are two young ladies sitting on crates with big smiles . The two seated girls smile towards the camera .
